data-triple-N3.o: "Stoke City Football Club are an English professional football club based in Stoke-on-Trent, Staffordshire that play in the Premier League. Founded in 1863, they are the oldest club in the Premier League, and are the second oldest professional football club in the world, after Notts County. The club play in the Premier League after winning promotion in 2008; prior to this Stoke had not participated in top flight football for twenty-three years."@en
